all 940-369-8284 to reserve a table. Online— UNT faculty/staff and students only and must be made on a campus computer. Go to https://aits-booking.unt.edu/reservation Gift Certificates Get Avesta gift certificates for yourself, friends or co-workers. The cost is only $10.70 each. Certificates include an entrée, soup or salad, and beverage. To purchase, visit the Dining Services office today.  Follow Us Tweets by @UNTdining Like Us University of North Texas Dining © 2017 A Mopro Website Back to Top 